reviews: Been purchasing Carhartt for years. This sweater is replacing one that has taken a beating for 5 years. 3rd wash in there is a separation in the seam on the right torso. I expect better than this from Carhartt. Missed the return window by 5 days. Brutal.
product_name: Carhartt Men's Midweight Hooded Zip Front Sweatshirt

reviews:
Purchased the Large/Tall version.
- Fit is great.
- Zipper is poor quality. It is not smooth and gets hung up sometimes.
- No loop to hang sewn in behind neck area.
- Looks and feels not much better than a Walmart sweater.

This is the first Carhartt product I have purchased which I am unhappy with. It's very nice that they are making tall versions of clothing now but I would spend more money and get a more expensive version next time.
Wash/dry twice before wearing anything dark as this thing sheds fluff like crazy.
product_name: Carhartt Men's Midweight Hooded Zip Front Sweatshirt

review_title: Good quality. Good Fit. Will buy again
reviews:
People mentioned that this item was over-sized so I bought a 2XLT instead of my usual 3XLT .
It fits tight - wish I had ordered my reg size.... NEXT time .. and there will be a next time because the quality is very good and I just like wearing it. Nice length on arms and hips, not to long at all!
Recommend this jacket!
product_name: Carhartt Men's Midweight Hooded Zip Front Sweatshirt

review_title: Tall size is main reason for using this company .
reviews: This about the 3rd or 4rth product I got from this company . The quality Is always very good and the material is always substantial (heavy) . The main reason I use this company is how it accomidates people with long torsos . For me 2xl is always short and big all over , but xl Tall is perfect .
product_name: Carhartt Men's Midweight Hooded Zip Front Sweatshirt

reviews: Fast shipping, was as described. Good quality as Carhartt always is. Its thick without being bulky and its light feeling but warm. I'm 5'11 200 I got the xl tall and fits fine maybe abit big next time I'll do a L tall or just xl and that would be a nicer fit for myself. Would buy again.
product_name: Carhartt Men's Midweight Hooded Zip Front Sweatshirt
